    "description": "# Customer Table Documentation\n## Business Context\nThe `customer` table captures essential information about customers within our financial services organization. This table serves as a centralized repository for customer details, enabling efficient management and analysis of customer data.\n### Example Business Context\nImagine a scenario where our organization needs to assess the performance of active customers with the highest balances. The `customer` table facilitates such analyses by providing a comprehensive view of customer-related metrics.\n## Technical Usage Information\nThe `customer` table is designed to support various business processes, including customer relationship management, financial reporting, and risk management. Below are the key technical details related to this table:\n",
